{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{countable|botany|usually }} A [[shrub]] or [[tree]] of the genus ''[[Acacia]]'', or from a species formerly classified in this genus, or believed to belong to the genus. {{defdate|First attested around 1350 to 1470.}}<ref name=SOED>Brown, Lesley, ed. ''The Shorter Oxford English Dictionary.'' 5th. Oxford: Oxford University Press, 2003.</ref>
