# [[false acacia|False acacia]]; [[robinia tree]], {{taxlink|Robinia pseudoacacia|binomial}}. {{defdate|First attested in the mid 17th century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{uncountable}} [[gum arabic|Gum arabic]]; [[gum acacia]]. {{defdate|First attested in the early 19th century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
